# Files

- README         : this file
- pdfboxes.dtx   : source file
- pdfboxes.ins   : install file
- pdfboxes.pdf   : documentation


# Installation
Itâ€™s recommended to use your package manager to install the
current version from CTAN. To install this package manually
download alls files and then navigate to the folder that
contains pdfboxes.ins.
Run

    latex pdfboxes.ins

to get the file pdfboxes.sty which should be moved somewhere
TeX can find it (e.g. $TEXMFHOME/tex/latex/pdfboxes/pdfboxes.sty)

To typeset the manual run

     pdflatex pdfboxes.dtx
     makeindex -s gglo.ist -o pdfboxes.gls pdfboxes.glo
     makeindex -s gind.ist -o pdfboxes.ind pdfboxes.idx
     pdflatex pdfboxes.dtx
     pdflatex pdfboxes.dtx
